        "description": "Engineering Director, Recommendation\n• In charge of whole recommendation AI and ML stacks powering Instagram and Facebook recommendations (Reels, in feeds recommendation, etc), ranging from retrieval model, ranking model, ML Infra, large scale GPU training and inference, cuda/triton Kernel optimization.\n• Leading recommendation innovation, and a rare person who deeply knows about both modeling, GPU and ML infra, a person who could do both deep hands-on IC work and org leader work (a 200 people team including both research scientist and engineers).\n▸ [Model/GPU Kernel] Generative recommender\n▸ [Model/GPU Kernel] Sequence modeling based on transformer arch\n▸ GPU based retrieval, RAG system\n▸ [Sharder/comm/dist training] thousands cards large scale GPU training\n▸ [GPU cuda kernel] GPU cuda kernel for index search, similarity vector search and learnable index\n▸ [Agentic] Innovation on agentic recommender based on LLM\n▸ [Multi-modal] Multi-modal content understanding based on LLM\n\n\n05/2016-11/2021\nDirector of Engineering, Head of Engineering, Facebook Search\n• Search Infra & Platform (Search Indexing; Index Serving (a.k.a Unicorn); ML Infra; Retrieval Platform for Meta; Embedding retrieval).\n• Search NLP — query understanding and content understanding by leveraging different NLP tech, improved FB Search quality by x%.\n• Search relevance (NLP, Computer vision, query understanding, document understanding, user understanding, ML ranking, whole page ranking, typeahead ranking).\n• Search product (client side, middle tier, product infra, foundation, search nullstate, speed, capacity, reliability, middle tier, etc).",
